venue.name: College Rock, Quincy Quarries, Crow Hill, Others

item.description: the weather is going to be beautiful!!! Pete from the Boston Rock Climbing Meetup is havinga group at Quincy Quarries on Saturdya and let me know so I could let Blackstone know. I might be heading to College Rock again, forsome tricky and sequency faves, and I bet there are others who want to make the trip to crow hill...check the message board and folllow the email trail! See you on the rock!
item.how_to_find_us: Follow the email trail, or, look for the red jetta, or maybe the white motorbike
